title: Did Biden Give Gitmo Prisoners COVID-19 Vaccines Before Americans?
subtitle: Doses were first sent to the Guantanamo Bay naval base before being dispersed to facilities across the military compound.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: U.S. President Joe Biden rolled out a plan to administer COVID-19 immunizations to detainees held at the Guantanamo Bay prison camp in Cuba before many Americans had received their first dose.
